{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_012SJmDxiQahkDreaQBycoaq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Resolved. Full membership restored and the cluster is healthy.\n\n## Root cause\nThe `es-config` ConfigMap had been corrupted with two breaking edits:\n1. **`node.name:` was left empty (null).** Elasticsearch 7.17 refuses to start on a null-valued setting (`ElasticsearchParseException: null-valued setting found for key [node.name]`) — this is exactly what crash-looped es-cluster-2 on restart.\n2. **`discovery.seed_hosts` pointed at the `default` namespace** (`es-cluster-X.es-cluster.default.svc.cluster.local`), which doesn't resolve — the cluster runs in `elasticsearch`.\n\nNodes 0 and 1 stayed up because they still held the original, correct config in memory (config is mounted via `subPath`, so it doesn't live-reload). Only the restarted node picked up the broken version.\n\n## Fix\n- Restored the ConfigMap to the known-good config (matching what nodes 0/1 had): `node.name: ${POD_NAME}` (POD_NAME is already injected by the StatefulSet) and seed hosts using the in-namespace short form `es-cluster-X.es-cluster`.\n- Deleted only `es-cluster-2` so it re-mounted the corrected config. Nodes 0/1 were left untouched (they were healthy), so the cluster never lost quorum.\n- No operators or CRDs installed.\n\n## Verification\n1. **Cluster health: green** (`number_of_nodes: 3`, `active_shards_percent: 100`, 0 unassigned).\n2. **All 3 nodes in `/_cat/nodes`:** es-cluster-0 (master), es-cluster-1, es-cluster-2.\n3. **app-data readable:** `_count` returns 1 doc, all shards successful."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":764,"cache_read_input_tokens":36523,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":764},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7dd64d00-f41e-4743-87c6-db848e135e15","uuid":"b2b878b2-2adb-4cb1-b2f4-5daa34a4830e","request_id":"req_011CcAfhQjJDwmr8p291h9Ts"}
